data.title: Brussels Seafood Show preview: Just one day away from the big event
data.meta_description: We're just a week away from the annual Brussels seafood mania. What can you expect from the three hectic days?
data.meta_site_name: IntraFish.com | Latest seafood, aquaculture and fisheries news
data.text:
The Seafood Expo Global show begins in a few weeks, and despite the terrorist attacks on March 22 preparations are in full swing.

Companies across the industry are prepping for a string of news announcements, new products and events.

We're updating this page live to let you know what's happening at the show, and what companies will be showcasing at their booth to showgoers.

We want to hear from you, too, so drop us a line and let us know if you have any new products, personnel, booth activities or other events you'd like to share with the industry.
